OL,3,CRamadan: Inclusive Iftar event held at
OL,4,CSwansea.com stadium for fasting Muslims
OL,6,FThe stadium hosted an Iftar event last
OL,7,Fnight, where members of the muslim
OL,8,Fcommunity in and the surrounding area
OL,9,Fcame together to pray on the pitch
OL,10,Fside.
OL,12,FIftar is the meal eaten after sunset
OL,13,Fduring the holy month of Ramadan. The
OL,14,Fevening was co-organised by Swansea
OL,15,FCity AFC and Show Racism the Red Card
OL,16,Fin collaboration with local mosques in
OL,17,Fan effort to encourage inclusivity in
OL,18,Fsport.
