OL,3,CRamadan: Inclusive Iftar event held at
OL,4,CSwansea.com stadium for fasting Muslims
OL,6,F"Football is definitely one of the
OL,7,Fmost inclusive games out there, you
OL,8,Fcan be all shapes and sizes, you can
OL,9,Fplay all different positions, I think
OL,10,Fthat's the beautiful part about it."
OL,12,FDean Pymble from Show Racism the Red
OL,13,FCard added: "Within sports there are
OL,14,Fthings that are improving, but there's
OL,15,Fa long way to go. The premier league
OL,16,Fallowing players observing Ramadan to
OL,17,Fbreak fast during games is really
OL,18,Fimportant.
