OL,3,CRamadan: Inclusive Iftar event held at
OL,4,CSwansea.com stadium for fasting Muslims
OL,6,F"But we're still seeing up and down
OL,7,Fthe country reports of racist
OL,8,Fincidents both at players but also
OL,9,Ftowards fans at games."
OL,11,FThis is the second time for an Iftar
OL,12,Fevening to be held at the stadium,
OL,13,Fwith also hosting a similar event last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FDr Mahaboob Basha BEM, who represents
OL,17,Fthe Mosque Consortium said he's
OL,18,Fnoticed an active effort to improve
OL,19,Fthe experience for muslims who attend
OL,20,Flocal matches.
