OL,3,CRamadan: Inclusive Iftar event held at
OL,4,CSwansea.com stadium for fasting Muslims
OL,6,F"The stadium said we now have an
OL,7,Fofficial space for muslim people to
OL,8,Fpray. During match time, you can get
OL,9,Fout from your stand to go and pray,
OL,10,Fwhich is a major step and major
OL,11,Fsupport for people who will be
OL,12,Fpraying."
OL,14,FWith over 100 people from the
OL,15,Fcommunity coming together to break
OL,16,Ffast, organisers hope the event will
OL,17,Fhave demonstrated the effort going
OL,18,Finto making sure sport locations are
OL,19,Finclusive to everyone.
